  "title": {
    "type": "text",
    "$t": "Activities during school holiday, Children Learning Community July 2024 Report "
  },
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "$t": "<p>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"FI\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: FI; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">Dear friends,</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt;\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Aptos; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">We thank our loyal friends for keeping the children learning community\nrun until today. Thank you for all your prayers and kind attention to the\nchildren. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">At the beginning of July,\nchildren spent their holiday with outdoor trip to Ragunan, visiting Educational\nFarm Center and the Zoo. </span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjZOff3Bl1_yfdyvfsssDR1tJAQswR2gWwSIFR8ZA9MKPtPNNGaJ8Il869YdPpk47IPJrsrWtxh5viRHx_eozrFOBpthfC-YRHZPp3Sd8XpGK9_lo5TZYJsbiGg1IJAsnphvQd9eoq1wCRTmqWnqdmI3hMAja2jhYsNRGf3myJ6xyMICwKf0w4IEBl6jlq8/s1440/keg.Ragunan0724.1.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1440\" data-original-width=\"1440\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjZOff3Bl1_yfdyvfsssDR1tJAQswR2gWwSIFR8ZA9MKPtPNNGaJ8Il869YdPpk47IPJrsrWtxh5viRHx_eozrFOBpthfC-YRHZPp3Sd8XpGK9_lo5TZYJsbiGg1IJAsnphvQd9eoq1wCRTmqWnqdmI3hMAja2jhYsNRGf3myJ6xyMICwKf0w4IEBl6jlq8/s320/keg.Ragunan0724.1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span><p></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">They were excited to\nobserve a new thing, outside their Cakung’s class. </span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">We thank facilitators, Mrs Arleta and her family, Mr.\nHeru and friends of big brother Asita who assist the children throughout the\noutdoor learning experience.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">In the middle of July 2024, when the school was about\nto start, we<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>got invited by the charity\nof orphan and underprivileged to their event.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span>The team of facilitators with 15 children attended this event at Bung\nKarno Sports Stadium’s mosque. </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhF3Dm826hMiL0elfcoG6Kk5avjJS46hxyF-f-kW-AmxPDXtSrAknim3OqIqMBBYfzX2cjLB6KlUarMdQ0vhA3U2DHtfJGQ-eiiyAHoJyHP9jdfITYfyhP098ON66xX-XtqAC3P5zWPcM1_E8L1ZAFySEvalO1Pw63Uy2Go0jJCdG31IlHlaGd0ghjxq6Le/s2080/AcaraSantunan0724-1.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1560\" data-original-width=\"2080\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhF3Dm826hMiL0elfcoG6Kk5avjJS46hxyF-f-kW-AmxPDXtSrAknim3OqIqMBBYfzX2cjLB6KlUarMdQ0vhA3U2DHtfJGQ-eiiyAHoJyHP9jdfITYfyhP098ON66xX-XtqAC3P5zWPcM1_E8L1ZAFySEvalO1Pw63Uy2Go0jJCdG31IlHlaGd0ghjxq6Le/s320/AcaraSantunan0724-1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><br /></span><p></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Cakung’s children thank big sister Qoriah and the\norganizer of this event for their kind attention. </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">During long holiday, the number of Cakung’s children\nwere increased and involved in various activities. We had 28 active children at\nthat time.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">We thank facilitators, Cakung and Ciawi’s\ncommunity mothers, the personnel of Cakung’s and Ciawi’s learning centre who\ndedicate their time to help us.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color: #500050; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Thank you for your faithful dedication to help the children\nand their activities. </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">Attached are pictures of July 2024 Cakung’s and Ciawi’s children’s\nlearning activities, the outdoor activity, healthy meal program and the\ninvolvement of our children at the charity event for the orphan and underprivileged\nchildren.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjWbyMpMXF7tfXLjML4tuIdbLPq-gJ1Ur8JNk6Kd0bJ1fpqrupXxbd8Dl0CMzXSn1jRCyxLQrDFrMAw_p4cRzyzDXBpa6EubkWMadsnUtRjEXifLo19BtCmZ8Zq5H1ueNCgvlm1o8LYnlAGxcCvJ11WfDmFAOEhW7PGcfWcWe-_oO2VfsmqHtUgYBAOqIkG/s2304/keg.belajar0724.1.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"2304\" data-original-width=\"2304\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjWbyMpMXF7tfXLjML4tuIdbLPq-gJ1Ur8JNk6Kd0bJ1fpqrupXxbd8Dl0CMzXSn1jRCyxLQrDFrMAw_p4cRzyzDXBpa6EubkWMadsnUtRjEXifLo19BtCmZ8Zq5H1ueNCgvlm1o8LYnlAGxcCvJ11WfDmFAOEhW7PGcfWcWe-_oO2VfsmqHtUgYBAOqIkG/s320/keg.belajar0724.1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjSQ__tzyfXYyi3YQv5jflFcAVfWAUwnw1AAiEBCqMcj-DUksHJSSHUhObTTQiq76nrwRC5w1DD8fvZSzy2qQ7jGLTn7gg2-JlTuw4FVZTujm_c1206JzZNHAMNThr6uGZaQS1z6Hb4CUwGNuRcVntncz5aT9qKKV9n1c3MusJvXjdCSqbfjb5fvLNy07Ku/s1440/Menusehat0724.1.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1440\" data-original-width=\"1440\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjSQ__tzyfXYyi3YQv5jflFcAVfWAUwnw1AAiEBCqMcj-DUksHJSSHUhObTTQiq76nrwRC5w1DD8fvZSzy2qQ7jGLTn7gg2-JlTuw4FVZTujm_c1206JzZNHAMNThr6uGZaQS1z6Hb4CUwGNuRcVntncz5aT9qKKV9n1c3MusJvXjdCSqbfjb5fvLNy07Ku/s320/Menusehat0724.1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div></span><p></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">We are thankful for all resolute donors who remember the children in\ntheir prayer, financial donations, and goods. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Children also would like to thank Mrs. Arleta and friends of big brother\nAsita for their clothing donations and gifts of books and stationery. Children\nalso grateful for donation of Elementary and Junior High textbooks from big\nbrother Justin.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br /></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"FI\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: FI; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">We pray for your health\nand prosperity. We are grateful for all your attention to the children all this\ntime and look forward to do many activities ahead.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt; mso-line-height-alt: 12.65pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">Attach is the August\n2024 Operation’s need. We have a very limited fund at this moment.</span></b><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">To fulfil the operational needs for the rest of 2024, we would like to\nask you to keep remember us in your monthly contribution.</span></b><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IN;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">It is our responsibility to give children the\nopportunity to be smart, independent and prosper in their own community. In\ndoing so, we participate in nation’s effort for social justice.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: IN; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Your kind attention and support are tremendous moral boost to us in\ncaring for these children. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IN;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">August&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IT;\">20</span></b><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IN;\">2</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">4</span></b><b><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: IT;\">&nbsp;Plan:\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 36pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; text-indent: -18pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-bidi-font-family: Aptos;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">Learning\nActivity </span></b><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; line-